{"pageProps":{"author":"Trigh Me","articles":[{"title":"UC Releases Additional Statement on AFSCME 3299 Strike","category":"Nexustentialism","subcategory":"Nexustentialism","publish_date":"2018-05-09T07:00:00.000Z","full_thumbnail":"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?resize=355%2C230&ssl=1","mobile_thumbnail":"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?resize=980%2C647&ssl=1","description":"The University of California has released an additional statement regarding their stance on the strike.","content":"<div class=\"single-post-content\">\n            <div id=\"attachment_53222\" style=\"width: 769px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-53222\" data-attachment-id=\"53222\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2013-11-25/this-week-in-photos-nov-18-24-2013/this-week-in-photos-1_11-24-2013_eric-swenson/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?fit=4246%2C2825&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"4246,2825\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"2.8\",\"credit\":\"Eric Swenson\",\"camera\":\"NIKON D700\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"1384933026\",\"copyright\":\"Eric Swenson\",\"focal_length\":\"28\",\"iso\":\"200\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0.008\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"1\"}' data-image-title=\"EARLY BIRD PROTESTERS\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Three striking members of the AFSCME 3299 union protest at Elings Hall near the Henley Gate on early Tuesday morning. That day saw workers and teaching assistants strike at all UC campuses to protest the UC administration’s management in recent months. &lt;em&gt;(Photo by Eric Swenson)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?fit=250%2C166&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?fit=888%2C591&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-53222\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson-250x166.jpg?resize=759%2C504\" alt=\"\" width=\"759\" height=\"504\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?resize=250%2C166&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?resize=1024%2C681&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?w=1776 1776w, https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/This-Week-in-Photos-1_11.24.2013_Eric-Swenson.jpg?w=2664 2664w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-53222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nexus File Photo</p></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The University of California has released an additional statement in response to the American Federation of State, County &amp; Municipal Employees (AFSCME) Local 3299’s three-day-long strike. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The strike, which began Monday morning, was organized  to protest low wages and has since gained impressive support from students and workers across the UC. It is suspected that the wide attention from local and statewide news outlets and the impact of the systemwide strike is what finally forced a direct response from the UC, as well as this additional clarifying statement.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“We honestly just don’t get it,” the UC stated in their befuddling proclamation. This is specifically in response to the report that collected data from UC employment records, which stated th